   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "6 (a). Pr(Grade A) = exp(beta0 + beta1*X1 + beta2*X2)/(1 + exp(beta0 + beta1*X1 + beta2*X2))\n",
    "so putting the values of beta0 = -6, beta1 = 0.05, beta2 = 1\n",
    "and, X1 = 40, X2 = 3.5\n",
    "Pr(Grade A) = 0.3775 or 37.75 %"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "79f6a848-cadf-4bbc-a247-260254d16546",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "(b) exp(beta0 + beta1*X1 + beta2*X2)/(1 + exp(beta0 + beta1*X1 + beta2*X2)) = 0.5\n",
    " => exp(beta0 + beta1*X1 + beta2*X2) = 1\n",
    " => beta0 + beta1*X1 + beta2*X2 = 0\n",
    " => No. of hours X1 = (-beta0 - beta2*X2)/beta1"
   ]
  }
 ],
